Note:
Runa Standard Library: Blockchain Dividends Distribution Module

Provides comprehensive dividend distribution mechanisms for tokenized assets and 
decentralized organizations. Implements enterprise-grade dividend distribution
protocols including automatic payouts, vesting schedules, tax withholding, and
multi-asset dividends. Competitive with production dividend implementations in
traditional finance systems, REITs, dividend-paying tokens, and DeFi protocols.

Features:
- Automated dividend distribution with snapshot mechanisms
- Multi-asset dividend support (tokens, ETH, stablecoins)
- Proportional distribution based on token holdings or custom weights
- Vesting schedules and time-locked dividend releases
- Tax withholding and regulatory compliance integration
- Dividend reinvestment programs (DRIPs) with compounding
- Claimable dividend pools with expiration management
- Historical dividend tracking and analytics
- Governance integration for dividend policy decisions
- Cross-chain dividend distribution coordination
- Dividend yield optimization and forecasting
- Anti-gaming mechanisms and snapshot protection
- Emergency dividend recovery and dispute resolution
- Institutional-grade reporting and audit trails
- Integration with treasury management and cash flow systems
:End Note

Note: Core Dividend Types
Type called "DividendSystem":
    dividend_config as DividendConfiguration
    token_registry as TokenRegistry
    distribution_engine as DistributionEngine
    snapshot_manager as SnapshotManager
    vesting_manager as VestingManager
    compliance_system as ComplianceSystem
    analytics_engine as AnalyticsEngine
    treasury_interface as TreasuryInterface
    governance_interface as GovernanceInterface
    emergency_system as EmergencySystem

Type called "DividendConfiguration":
    base_token as String
    dividend_assets as List[String]
    distribution_frequency as DistributionFrequency
    minimum_holding_period as Integer
    tax_withholding_enabled as Boolean
    automatic_distribution as Boolean
    drip_enabled as Boolean
    snapshot_protection_enabled as Boolean

